 nostalgic spell as I caught up with my old Clash of Clans account. So here is a breakdown of the top five video games that I have been playing during quarantine.</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_94355\" style=\"width: 486px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg\" data-slb-active=\"1\" data-slb-asset=\"261652931\" data-slb-internal=\"0\" data-slb-group=\"94354\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94355\" data-attachment-id=\"94355\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-05-09/a-list-of-fun-5-video-games-to-get-you-through-quarantine/nba-2k20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?fit=1000%2C1000&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"NBA-2K20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?fit=250%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?fit=888%2C888&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94355\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=476%2C476\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=250%2C250&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=260%2C260&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=100%2C100&amp;ssl=1 100w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=32%2C32&amp;ssl=1 32w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=64%2C64&amp;ssl=1 64w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=96%2C96&amp;ssl=1 96w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=128%2C128&amp;ssl=1 128w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=912%2C912&amp;ssl=1 912w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=550%2C550&amp;ssl=1 550w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/NBA-2K20.jpeg?resize=470%2C470&amp;ssl=1 470w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-94355\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Courtesy of GameStop</p></div>\n<p><b>NBA 2K20 &amp; MLB The Show 20</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Each sports game is unique in terms of which sport you want to play, but not in overall gameplay mechanics. Therefore, the choice of sports games all depends on the player. Do you like basketball or baseball? Well, look no further than </span><a href=\"https://nba.2k.com/en-US/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">NBA 2K20</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><a href=\"https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/mlb-the-show-20-ps4/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MLB The Show 20</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, the present league standards in virtual basketball and baseball entertainment. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yet in my opinion, the best sports game out there is </span><a href=\"https://www.ea.com/games/fifa/fifa-20\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIFA 20</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, the current contender in virtual soccer. It’s the most realistic of any sports game I’ve ever played, with awesome fluidity in ball dribbling, play making and, of course, goal scoring. (Make sure to turn the narrator language to Spanish because nothing beats the roaring, “Goooooaaaaallllll!” when you score.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only does a sports game virtually create the irony of attending a live match while </span><a href=\"https://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/29072667/agency-coronavirus-cancel-nearly-half-scheduled-sports-events-2020\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">most sports are being canceled</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, but UCSB has recently </span><a href=\"https://recreation.ucsb.edu/intramural-sports\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">implemented online intramural games</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> using 2K, Rocket League and FIFA. </span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_94356\" style=\"width: 806px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg\" data-slb-active=\"1\" data-slb-asset=\"206709340\" data-slb-internal=\"0\" data-slb-group=\"94354\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94356\" data-attachment-id=\"94356\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-05-09/a-list-of-fun-5-video-games-to-get-you-through-quarantine/cod-warzone/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?fit=1920%2C720&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1920,720\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"COD warzone\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?fit=250%2C94&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?fit=888%2C333&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94356\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?resize=796%2C299\" alt=\"\" width=\"796\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?resize=250%2C94&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?resize=1024%2C384&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?resize=768%2C288&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?resize=1536%2C576&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/COD-warzone.jpeg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-94356\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Courtesy of PlayStation</p></div>\n<p><b>Call of Duty: Warzone</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Up next is a newer video game that mimics the style of battle royal games like Fortnite, but utilizes Call of Duty’s revamped combat system: </span><a href=\"https://www.callofduty.com/warzone\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Call of Duty: Warzone</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This free-to-play game gives a new meaning to the phrase, “last man standing.” No matter what game mode you play, Warzone starts in an airplane with your teammates. The intro is characterized by an obvious “get ready to fricken’ jump” aesthetic that makes </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2BnOebsDtAQ\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tom Cruise’s “Mission Impossible” skydive stunt</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> look like a cakewalk.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Warzone is an absolute roller coaster with unlimited parachutes, many vantage points and a massive in-game map. You can traverse through skyscrapers like Batman or sneak through abandoned complexes like a navy seal </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">—</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> all from the comfort of your couch. </span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_94357\" style=\"width: 415px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg\" data-slb-active=\"1\" data-slb-asset=\"1319534437\" data-slb-internal=\"0\" data-slb-group=\"94354\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94357\" data-attachment-id=\"94357\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-05-09/a-list-of-fun-5-video-games-to-get-you-through-quarantine/minecraft/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?fit=431%2C600&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"431,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"minecraft\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?fit=180%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?fit=431%2C600&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94357\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?resize=405%2C564\" alt=\"\" width=\"405\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?w=431&amp;ssl=1 431w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/minecraft.jpeg?resize=180%2C250&amp;ssl=1 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 405px) 100vw, 405px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-94357\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Courtesy of Xbox</p></div>\n<p><b>Minecraft</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Minecraft, though released over a decade ago, continues to surpass expectations and supply endless creativity. With every passing year, more and more is added into the Minecraft universe due to the </span><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/Minecraft/comments/4yoo29/i_calculated_the_amount_of_possible_minecraft/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">almost-infinite amount of possible worlds</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, as well as the </span><a href=\"https://www.pcgamesn.com/minecraft/minecraft-player-count\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ever-growing number of monthly players</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, the real reason that Minecraft is on my list is because of the recent in-game creativity from our fellow Gauchos due to the increase in free time. The </span><a href=\"http://dailynexus.com/2020-04-08/ucsb-minecraft-server-building-a-home-away-from-home/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1:1 ratio Minecraft world of our lovely UCSB campus</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> was spearheaded by fourth-year Charles Neumann. You can even </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2373510656083495/?epa=SEARCH_BOX\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">log on</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and add to the growing minecraft campus. The overall creative and collaborative feel of Minecraft makes it an excellent game to use for connection, without the risk of going outside.</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_94358\" style=\"width: 418px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg\" data-slb-active=\"1\" data-slb-asset=\"924584948\" data-slb-internal=\"0\" data-slb-group=\"94354\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94358\" data-attachment-id=\"94358\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-05-09/a-list-of-fun-5-video-games-to-get-you-through-quarantine/ffvii/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?fit=1400%2C1744&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1400,1744\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"FFVII\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?fit=201%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?fit=822%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94358\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?resize=408%2C509\" alt=\"\" width=\"408\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?w=1400&amp;ssl=1 1400w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?resize=201%2C250&amp;ssl=1 201w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?resize=822%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 822w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?resize=768%2C957&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/FFVII.jpg?resize=1233%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 408px) 100vw, 408px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-94358\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Courtesy of PlayStation</p></div>\n<p><b>Final Fantasy VII Remake</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Forging ahead, we have the newest video game in this entire list — a gorgeous remastered version of a 1997 classic that remains a hit: </span><a href=\"https://ffvii-remake.square-enix-games.com/en-us\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Final Fantasy VII Remake</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many consider FFVII to be one of the best video games ever made, and I gotta say that I entirely agree. The new extended story gives depth where previously there were plot holes. The battle mechanics are excellent, the graphics are top notch, the voice acting is Oscar worthy, the plot is astonishing and the gameplay is incredible. I can go on and on about how good FFVII is. Still, the primary reason why this game is in such high personal regards is the fact that it’s the first of an entire </span><a href=\"https://screenrant.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-part-2-confirmed-development/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">planned series of Final Fantasy VII remakes</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, giving gamers something to look forward to as the days of social distancing continue.</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_94359\" style=\"width: 678px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg\" data-slb-active=\"1\" data-slb-asset=\"471833635\" data-slb-internal=\"0\" data-slb-group=\"94354\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94359\" data-attachment-id=\"94359\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-05-09/a-list-of-fun-5-video-games-to-get-you-through-quarantine/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?fit=1920%2C1080&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1920,1080\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?fit=250%2C141&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?fit=888%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94359\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?resize=668%2C376\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?resize=250%2C141&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?resize=1024%2C576&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/animal-crossing-new-horizons-switch-hero.jpg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-94359\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Courtesy of Nintendo</p></div>\n<p><b>Animal Crossing: New Horizons</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Last but not least, we have a game that makes being on a deserted island fun and cute — </span><a href=\"https://www.animal-crossing.com/new-horizons/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Animal Crossing: New Horizons</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every day, Animal Crossing: New Horizons provides a new list of tasks filled with gardening, town development, interior design, fishing, bug catching, loan repayment and fossil excavating that is sure to keep you busy and entertained throughout the quarantine. New Horizons is the perfect tropical getaway amid quarantine. It’s fun, purposeful, satisfying… and did I mention how cute it is?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And there you have it — five of the best video games that will hold you softly and whisper, “It’s gonna be all right,” throughout this quarantine. I’m personally going to be mostly playing Animal Crossing: New Horizons, but regardless of which one of the games mentioned above you choose, you are bound to stay sane and entertained for the months to come.</span></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peter Figueira thinks Animal Crossing: New Horizons is cute.</span></i></p>\n<div class=\"h5ab-print-button-container\"><div class=\"h5ab-print-button h5ab-print-button-left\" style=\"cursor: pointer; color: #555\"><i class=\"fa fa-print fa-lg\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Print</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" itemscope itemprop=\"author\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b68b686e8f70391f6b047ace6acaf69e?s=100&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\" srcset=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b68b686e8f70391f6b047ace6acaf69e?s=200&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\" class=\"avatar avatar-100 photo\" height=\"100\" width=\"100\" itemprop=\"image\"></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-authorname\"><a href=\"https://dailynexus.com/author/peterfigueira/\" class=\"vcard author\" rel=\"author\" itemprop=\"url\"><span class=\"fn\" itemprop=\"name\">Peter Figueira</span></a></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-desc\"><div itemprop=\"description\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Peter Figueira is an opinion writer double majoring in communication and film &amp; media studies. He loves music, movies, video games and comedy.</span></p>\n</div></div><div class=\"clearfix\"></div><div class=\"saboxplugi